_DeChambeau\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"DeChambeau\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13156709\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bryson_DeChambeau\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bryson_DeChambeau\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the top six in three major championships\", \"from\": 525, \"to\": 565}, {\"ngram\": \"Clark\", \"from\": 577, \"to\": 582}, {\"ngram\": \"the cut\", \"from\": 590, \"to\": 597}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In the one major where Clark made the cut\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094the U.S. Open\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094DeChambeau was the winner.\", \"from\": 608, \"to\": 694, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the one major\", \"from\": 611, \"to\": 624}, {\"ngram\": \"Clark\", \"from\": 631, \"to\": 636}, {\"ngram\": \"the cut\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094the U.S.\", \"from\": 642, \"to\": 660}, {\"ngram\": \"the winner\", \"from\": 683, \"to\": 693}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It is under that backdrop that Clark arrived outside of Paris looking to get back to the form he showed earlier this year when he won at Pebble Beach and contended at both the Arnold Palmer Invitational and Players Championship\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094finishing second at both to Scottie Scheffler.\", \"from\": 696, \"to\": 972, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 752, \"end\": 757, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.996847393761965, \"rank\": 0.0031625765966644785, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 954, \"end\": 971, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Scottie_Scheffler\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Scottie Scheffler\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13156709\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Scottie_Scheffler\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Scottie_Scheffler\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"that backdrop\", \"from\": 708, \"to\": 721}, {\"ngram\": \"Clark\", \"from\": 727, \"to\": 732}, {\"ngram\": \"the form\", \"from\": 781, \"to\": 789}, {\"ngram\": \"Pebble Beach\", \"from\": 833, \"to\": 845}, {\"ngram\": \"both the Arnold Palmer Invitational\", \"from\": 863, \"to\": 898}, {\"ngram\": \"Players\", \"from\": 903, \"to\": 910}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cIt\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s been a unique year,\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d Clark said Wednesday in advance of the tournament.\", \"from\": 974, \"to\": 1057, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a unique year\", \"from\": 989, \"to\": 1002}, {\"ngram\": \"Clark\", \"from\": 1007, \"to\": 1012}, {\"ngram\": \"advance\", \"from\": 1031, \"to\": 1038}, {\"ngram\": \"the tournament\", \"from\": 1042, \"to\": 1056}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cI started out fantastic and in previous years on Tour, I typically have kind of played better at the end or the year.\", \"from\": 1058, \"to\": 1178, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cI\", \"from\": 1058, \"to\": 1062}, {\"ngram\": \"previous years\", \"from\": 1092, \"to\": 1106}, {\"ngram\": \"Tour\", \"from\": 1110, \"to\": 1114}, {\"ngram\": \"the end\", \"from\": 1158, \"to\": 1165}, {\"ngram\": \"the year\", \"from\": 1169, \"to\": 1177}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cBut I kind of have some injuries I have been dealing with, happened right before Houston leading into the Masters, and I have not been the same.\", \"from\": 1180, \"to\": 1327, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1264, \"end\": 1271, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Houston\", \"score\": 0.9702483652422303, \"rank\": 0.025985570495781193, \"text\": \"Houston\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Houston\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Houston\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"some injuries\", \"from\": 1202, \"to\": 1215}, {\"ngram\": \"the Masters\", \"from\": 1285, \"to\": 1296}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I feel like I am finally getting to where I can swing at the level that I know I can swing, and so that's kind of been an ongoing issue and it's been frustrating for me.\", \"from\": 1328, \"to\": 1497, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the level\", \"from\": 1385, \"to\": 1394}, {\"ngram\": \"an ongoing issue\", \"from\": 1447, \"to\": 1463}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cThen I have got to be honest, I have been very frustrated with how I played at the majors.\", \"from\": 1499, \"to\": 1592, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the majors\", \"from\": 1581, \"to\": 1591}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I believe that I wasn't showing how good of a player I know I can be, and especially at highest level in the majors.\", \"from\": 1593, \"to\": 1709, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a player\", \"from\": 1637, \"to\": 1645}, {\"ngram\": \"especially at highest level\", \"from\": 1667, \"to\": 1694}, {\"ngram\": \"the majors\", \"from\": 1698, \"to\": 1708}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But I have also got to look at how far I have come in two years.\", \"from\": 1710, \"to\": 1774, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"two years\", \"from\": 1764, \"to\": 1773}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I am fifth on the FedEx in back-to-back years and I have won multiple times and I have a lot of top finishes and I am here at the Olympics.\", \"from\": 1775, \"to\": 1914, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1793, \"end\": 1798, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/FedEx\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.6200350081072666e-20, \"text\": \"FedEx\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/FedEx\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/FedEx\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"back\", \"from\": 1810, \"to\": 1814}, {\"ngram\": \"multiple times\", \"from\": 1836, \"to\": 1850}, {\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 1862, \"to\": 1867}, {\"ngram\": \"top finishes\", \"from\": 1871, \"to\": 1883}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 1901, \"to\": 1913}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cSo I have got to make sure I do not let the outside people put too much pressure on myself because I have grown so much in these two years.\", \"from\": 1916, \"to\": 2058, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the outside people\", \"from\": 1959, \"to\": 1977}, {\"ngram\": \"too much pressure\", \"from\": 1982, \"to\": 1999}, {\"ngram\": \"these two years\", \"from\": 2042, \"to\": 2057}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's not where I want to be in the future, but years like this, I have learned a lot and I am hoping I take all the things I learned and play better in the majors next year.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d The other U.S. Open champions in the field are Spain\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s Jon Rahm (2021) and England\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s Matt Fitzpatrick (2022).\", \"from\": 2059, \"to\": 2350, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2326, \"end\": 2342, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matt_Fitzpatrick\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Matt Fitzpatrick\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13156709\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matt_Fitzpatrick\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matt_Fitzpatrick\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the future\", \"from\": 2090, \"to\": 2100}, {\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 2138, \"to\": 2143}, {\"ngram\": \"all the things\", \"from\": 2167, \"to\": 2181}, {\"ngram\": \"the majors\", \"from\": 2211, \"to\": 2221}, {\"ngram\": \"The other U.S. Open champions\", \"from\": 2236, \"to\": 2265}, {\"ngram\": \"the field\", \"from\": 2269, \"to\": 2278}, {\"ngram\": \"Spain\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s\", \"from\": 2283, \"to\": 2292}, {\"ngram\": \"Jon Rahm\", \"from\": 2293, \"to\": 2301}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Clark won last year at Los Angeles Country Club and added the victory earlier this year at Pebble Beach.\", \"from\": 2351, \"to\": 2455, \"entities\"